      'short_description' => '["This product is part of the Easy modicon M100 range, an offer of logic controllers for simple machines up to 40 I\\/O. This logic controller provides 4 fast inputs, 2 high speed inputs, 3 regular inputs and 7 normally opened relay outputs","This product is part of the Easy modicon M100 range, an offer of logic controllers for simple machines up to 40 I\\/O. This logic controller provides 4 fast inputs, 2 high speed inputs, 3 regular inputs and 7 normally opened relay outputs","This product is part of the Easy modicon M100 range, an offer of logic controllers for simple machines up to 40 I\\/O. This logic controller provides 4 fast inputs, 2 high speed inputs, 3 regular inputs and 7 normally opened relay outputs","This product is part of the Easy modicon M100 range, an offer of logic controllers for simple machines up to 40 I\\/O. This logic controller provides 4 fast inputs, 2 high speed inputs, 3 regular inputs and 7 normally opened relay outputs","This product is part of the Easy modicon M100 range, an offer of logic controllers for simple machines up to 40 I\\/O. This logic controller provides 4 fast inputs, 2 high speed inputs, 3 regular inputs and 7 normally opened relay outputs","This product is part of the Easy modicon M100 range, an offer of logic controllers for simple machines up to 40 I\\/O. This logic controller provides 4 fast inputs, 2 high speed inputs, 3 regular inputs and 7 normally opened relay outputs","This product is part of the Easy modicon M100 range, an offer of logic controllers for simple machines up to 40 I\\/O. This logic controller provides 4 fast inputs, 2 high speed inputs, 3 regular inputs and 7 normally opened relay outputs","This product is part of the Easy modicon M100 range, an offer of logic controllers for simple machines up to 40 I\\/O. This logic controller provides 4 fast inputs, 2 high speed inputs, 3 regular inputs and 7 normally opened relay outputs"]',
      'description' => '<p><span style="font-weight: bolder;">This product</span>&nbsp;is part of the<font color="#ff0000">&nbsp;Easy</font>&nbsp;modicon M100 range, an offer of logic controllers for simple machines up to 40 I/O. This logic controller provides 4 fast inputs, 2 high speed inputs, 3 regular inputs and 7 normally opened relay outputs.</p><p>It is an Easy Modicon logic controller with an input voltage of 24V DC, an output voltage of 24V DC, 220V AC and an output current of 2A. Easy to maintain and update with its micro SD memory card. Integrated connections are USB port with mini B USB 2.0 connector, non isolated serial link 1 and RS485 interface and non isolated serial link 2 and RS232/RS485 interface. It is a controller with an internal flash of 512KB and a micro SD card capacity of 32GB. It is an IP20 rated product. Its dimensions are 110mm (Width) x 70mm (Depth) x 90mm (Height). It weighs 0.295kg. Designed for automation of small finishing, production, assembly or packaging machines. This product is certified by CE. It meets EN/IEC 61010-2-201 and EN/IEC 61131-2 standards. It supports DIN rail mount. Entry-level plc perfectly suited to meet specific needs of emerging markets at an affordable price without compromise. Cost-effective and easy solution to sequential control needs for your simple machines up to 40 I/O.</p>',
