     'attributes' => 
    array (
      'id' => 5,
      'name' => 'M262PLC',
      'price' => 11,
      'category_id' => 10,
      'brand_id' => 4,
      'images' => '"[\\"20260206_131904_6985ea485b127.jpg\\"]"',
      'short_description' => '["DIGITIZATION: integrate your machine in any environment \\u201ccloud & on premise\\u201d, with Direct connectivity to cloud services","FLEXIBILITY: Automation A la carte with Smart Communication Modules, Scalable performances with Modicon TM3\\/5 IO modules","EFFICIENCY with Smart Engineering design: Benefit from Sercos , real time fieldbus for fast motion and safety control","PROTECTION with Embedded Safety, Cybersecurity (encrypted communication, network separation, Achilles certification)","Modicon M262 are validated as a Green Premium product, getting all Eco-label criteria set by Schneider Electric"]',
      'description' => '<section class="section section--with-columns" style="box-sizing: inherit; padding: 56px 10px 72px; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0px auto 8px; display: flex; flex-direction: row;"><div class="section__content" style="box-sizing: inherit; width: 780px;"><pes-description class="description dark hydrated"><div class="text-container pdp-long-desc expanded" style="margin: unset; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem; display: -webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp: unset; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; overflow: hidden; text-align: justify;"><span class="description__content font-m" style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(98, 100, 105); width: 780px;">Modicon M262 logic/motion controllers are designed for performance-demanding machines, IIoT-ready and combine logic, motion and safety control applications. TM262L20MESE8T is specialized in the logic control of 4 fast digital inputs and 4&nbsp;fast digital ouputs. It controls motion with independant axis in EtherNet/IP. This logic controller embeds two Ethernet-based networks (EtherNet/IP, Modbus/TCP), one serial port (Modbus, ASCII, Machine Expert protocols). Modicon M262 are logic/motion controllers with embedded cloud connectivity, figuring cybersecurity capabilities, supporting monitoring, analytics and predictive maintenance. It is powered with a non-isolated 24V DC power supply, has a built-in overload protection, embeds a dual-core processor, reaches a 5ns/instruction performance. This logic controller has one communication bus (Ethernet, CANopen), one IO bus, one IO port. It measures 125mm width, 90mm depth, and 100 mm height. It weighs 0.665kg. This controller is designed for machinery requiring integrated IIoT connectivity or encrypted communication. Certified with CE, cULus HazLoc, RCM, EAC, Achilles L2, EU RO Mutual, Conform to UL 61010-1/-2-201, CSAC22.2 No. 61010-1/-2-201, ANSI/ISA 12-12-01, EN 61131-2. This controller is compatible with TMS CANopen smart communication module, Modicon TM3 IO expansion modules, and configured by EcoStruxure Machine Expert. Modicon M262 logic controller installs on 35mm DIN rail with Clip-on locks. Modicon M262 logic/motion controllers are the IIoT-ready controllers for performance machines. Modicon M262 logic/motion controllers embed Industrial Internet of Things (IIoT) protocols and encryption to provide direct cloud connectivity &amp; digital services.</span></div></pes-description></div></section>',
